| Packet Type | Signed? | Encrypted? | Reason |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `PT_REGISTER` | ✅ Yes | ✅ Yes | Identity verification |
| `PT_INTRO_REQUEST` | ❌ No | ✅ Yes | Low risk, needs privacy |
